{"tid":957752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"更勝麻藥搜查官　巨乳女警脫掉制服「想被逮捕」","createTime":"2018-12-27T09:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:54:26.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89ae90f546395725a4f224fe4137e5b6908acf33","tid":957752,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZ2B9QD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZ2B9QD.png&h=731eb4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EN1joaE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEN1joaE.png&h=9d2c0a05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVpQuQF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVpQuQF.png&h=c44b66a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一名27歲女生肯特曼(Sermin Kentmen)，被當地網路鄉民封為「巨乳女警」，她擁有麻藥搜查官的魔鬼身材，讓不少鄉民直呼「想被她逮捕」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，肯特曼的Instagram上，貼出不少穿著警察制服的照片，還有更多的爆乳性感照。脫掉警察制服的肯特曼，正努力成為一名網紅，她在網路上時常PO出自己健身有成的照片和影片，當然也少不了清涼的比基尼影像，網友紛紛直呼：「想被逮捕。」、「如果她當警察，一定要向她認罪。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，目前有2千粉絲追隨肯特曼的Instagram，而她的父親也是名前員警，她在18歲時就加入警察行列，不過《太陽報》打到警局詢問，表示目前肯特曼已經離職。"},{"pid":"78870dfcc015753413f00071f036f5324a4b365c","tid":957752,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b300667907ac9f80d49a104e6a966bbb97936b49","tid":957752,"uid":126219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"快d逮捕我"},{"pid":"ff284f5678f3c7847e4241d09e8d11d90400801a","tid":957752,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"19591f1d9f600fcfec14ab50c17942b5b220503b","tid":957752,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}